<h1 class="page-header">Privacy Policy</h1>
<p><a href="https://www.ioshopping.co.za">IOShopping.co.za</a> Privacy Policy has been compiled to reflect that of the Protection of Personal Information Act also known as the <a href="https://popia.co.za/">POPIA</a>  Act. The Act applies to any person or organisation who keeps any type of records relating to the personal information of anyone, unless those records are subject to other legislation which protects such information for example the Personally Identifiable Information (PII) Act and <a href="https://www.popiact-compliance.co.za/gdpr-information/31-lessons-learnt-from-gdpr">General Data Protection Regulations (GDPR)</a>. The <a href="#">Electronics Communications and Transactions ACT,</a> 2002 (ECT) provides for the facilitation and regulation of Electronic Communications and Transactions.</p>

<p>It therefore sets the minimum standards for the <a href="https://popia.co.za/section-1-definitions/">protection of personal information</a>. It regulates the “processing” of personal information. “Processing” includes collecting, receiving, recording, organizing, retrieving, or using such information; or disseminating, distributing or making such personal information available.  Refer to Section 2, <a href="https://popia.co.za/section-2-purpose-of-act/">"Purpose of Act"</a> The Act will also relate to records which are already in the possession of the entity or person doing the processing. YOU are therefore advised to review the privacy policy carefully to better understand how <a href="https://www.ioshopping.co.za">IOShopping.co.za</a> collects, utilizes and protects YOUR Personal Information collected on our website.
</p>


